WEBVTT

00:18.519 --> 00:21.522
That gentleman
and his daughter,
the money they took,

00:21.622 --> 00:23.491
ain't never coming back.

00:23.591 --> 00:26.660
We're going to recreate
my father's system here
without my father.

00:26.760 --> 00:29.597
A consortium with all of you
sharing in the profits.

00:29.697 --> 00:32.100
I'll do that the moment you
lift the ban on Captain Vane.

00:32.200 --> 00:33.434
Charles Vane is an animal.

00:33.534 --> 00:35.503
You have until dark
to come to your senses.

00:35.603 --> 00:37.438
Do you have some problem
with us holding onto
that whore?

00:37.538 --> 00:39.540
