Mr. Guthrie's orders
were explicit.

01:14.375 --> 01:16.777
No matter what,
I was to make sure that
you were on this ship.

01:16.877 --> 01:19.046
"I sent a message
to the captain of
the Scarborough.

01:19.147 --> 01:22.250
